parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Failure and Unavailability of Recall Repair Parts
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities. The unavailability of recall repair parts for an extended period poses a significant risk to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: None
as the issue is related to the unavailability of recall repair parts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manufacturer to provide timely recall repairs and parts can lead to a prolonged period of risk to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: None
as the issue is related to the manufacturer's response to the recall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a potential issue with the airbag system, which can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the check engine light comes on
the stability track and traction control lights come on
the vehicle shakes or jerks
the engine power is reduced
the airbag and seatbelt lights come on
the instrument console and/or entertainment console do not function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the check engine light comes on
the stability track and traction control lights come on
the vehicle shakes or jerks
the engine power is reduced
the airbag and seatbelt lights come on.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuse Box and Electrical Component Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuse box and electrical components can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the check engine light comes on
the stability track and traction control lights come on
the vehicle shakes or jerks
the engine power is reduced
the airbag and seatbelt lights come on
smoke comes out of the vents
the rear power liftgate becomes inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag and safety system can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly or fail to deploy in an accident, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag and seatbelt lights come on
the service airbag light comes on intermittently
the airbag system error message displays on the driver information center.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and hard shifting can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injury or death.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle jerks or shudders when shifting
the transmission shifts hard or abruptly
the vehicle experiences a delay in shifting
the transmission fails to shift into gear
the vehicle's engine RPMs race or fluctuate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure to engage can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injury or death.
symptoms: The transmission fails to engage into gear
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly when in park or neutral
the vehicle shifts into reverse gear unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission software issues can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injury or death.
symptoms: The transmission software patch is applied but does not resolve the issue
the transmission still experiences slipping or hard shifting after software update.
